Media Statement 12 June 2022 The Sunday Times article published on 12 June 2022 under the headline “Big ‘DIY tender’ for Chief Justice top brass” refers. As stated to the Sunday Times, the OCJ is currently in the process of gathering all relevant information relating to the matter and is taking legal advice. At the appropriate time, the OCJ will inform the public on the matter. We can assure the public that the State funds relating to this matter are safe. In view of this, the OCJ will not at this stage be making further comments or providing any additional information in this regard. Issued by the Office of the Chief Justice, 12 June 2022